            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/672.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grind the<strong> fennel seeds</strong> finely in a <strong>pestle and mortar</strong></p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>fennel seeds</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>,<strong>&nbsp;Dijon mustard</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>basil leaves</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> - this is your dressing&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
